Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:33.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}於是牽住了夥伴的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:39.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}這樣的話將永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:43.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年無憂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:51.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論如何都想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:57.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}夥伴們曾牽在一起的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:04.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已變得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:08.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一個個漸漸離去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:15.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}向著那甦醒之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:24.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}邁開腳步毅然前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:33.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}彷彿節日的喧囂過後
